Pahalgam Terrorist Attack: Pakistan's use of terrorism as a state policy and massacre of innocent civilians

One year ago, on April 22, 2025, the beautiful scenic views of Pahalgam witnessed something tragic, unforgiving and hateful. Pahalgam was shattered by bursts of gunfire and the horrified screams of those who had come to make peaceful memories with their loved ones. 

Today, the valley lies silent, with echoes of those screams lingering in the air. Reflecting on the anniversary of the Pahalgam attack, let us mourn those innocent lives lost to terrorism and reflect on what really took place on that dreadful day.

